I did the simple hack on the RS 12-469. It doesn&#39;t have a speaker so I connected it to my stereo amp and speakers. The sound was then pickd up by my optical microphone and recorded to an Olympus recorder.

&quot;We&#39;re thrilled that you will translate&quot;

&quot;Erland will make you gravity&quot;

&quot;You know what/why Heaven&#39;s a gate?&quot;

&quot;Tesla eliminated Tesla/extra filter&quot;

&quot;Now talk through....Grampa was missing Cedrick....Cedrick (louder)&quot;

&quot;We&#39;ve been watching him, he never closes a flue&quot; (I checked and the flue here was accidently left open)

Dave



